Use this script to quickly reorder multi-level terminals (MLTs) in Eplan P8.

Install in P8 by going to "Utilities/Scripts/Load" and browse to the script's location.

Once loaded, it will add two new menus under "Utilities": 

-Set Sort Code
-Reset Sort Code

Plase see http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hlBHK4pGKzY for an example of how to use it.